#''(Obsolete):'' To cast off or down; hence, to [[abase]]; to [[degrade]]; to lower; to [[debase]] - [[Donne]]
===Noun===
#''(Obsolete):'' A person in the lowest and most [[despicable]] condition; a [[castaway]]
